--- Astrotrain ---

Astrotrain arrives and lands beside the downed ship. He opens a 
commlink to Megatron, "Lord Megatron, we have reached the signal, and 
are awaiting response." He says to Cyclonus, through his speaker in 
an irritated voice, "Tell them to hurry up, we don't have all day..." 
His hatch opens.
